'''阿齐济耶省'''（{{lang-ar|'''العزيزيه '''}} ''Al ʿAzīzīyah''）是[[利比亚|利比亚]]的一个[[利比亚行政区划|省]]，位于利比亚西北部。首府[[阿齐济耶|阿齐济耶]]，2001年成为[[吉法拉省|吉法拉省]]的一部分<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20061015234155/http://www.gpc.gov.ly/online_alshabyat/index.php?sh=20 "شعبية الجفارة" ("Districts of Libya: Al Jfara")]  Website of the General People's Committee of Libya, from [[Internet_Archive|Internet Archive]] dated 18 April 2006</ref>
==气候==
在1922年9月13日, 气温纪录{{convert|57.8|C|abbr=on|1}}<ref>[http://ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/globalextremes.html Global Measured Extremes of Temperature and Precipitation.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507032709/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/globalextremes.html |date=2009-05-07 }} [[National_Climatic_Data_Center|National Climatic Data Center]], accessed 3 December 2008</ref> 是坐落在利比亚的阿齐济耶省。 这是{{Tsl|en|List_of_weather_records|气候纪录}}中地球上最热的地方。<ref>[http://www.gsfc.nasa.gov/scienceques2001/20020524.htm "What is the highest temperature recorded on Earth, and what's a reasonable upper limit on the Earth's temperature?"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060517193522/http://www.gsfc.nasa.gov/scienceques2001/20020524.htm |date=2006-05-17 }} Goddard Space Flight Center, National Aeronautics and Space Administration ([[NASA|NASA]]), accessed 7 September 2009</ref>

该气象纪录是在利比亚的[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]] (1551-1911)之后开始被记载。在利比亚气象中心(LNMC)气候指挥部的很多旧的气象站有足够的证据证明该地区是地球上最热的地方。

